VOLUME 
Volume wani indicators ne dayake Accumulating na transaction between buyers/sellers) volume Yana daukan kowanne time frame Amma mostly traders sunfi amfani dashi Akan 24 trading 
 VOLUME Yana nuna strength ko weak na price movement zuwa uptrend/downtrend  reversal/continuation
VOLUME IN TECHNICAL ANALYSIS 
Volume Yana daga cikin technical analysis indicators Wanda suke indicating zuwa ga entry/exiting point 
ANALYST 
Mostly traders  (analyst) suna amfani da tsayi/gajarta na Bar chart  wajen identifying adadi na    volume  da yayi accumulation A 24hours
idan volume Yana increasing lokacin da price yake moving  up/down ana considering amatsayin price movement with strength
VOLUME SUPPORT/RESISTANCE
Lokacin da Price yataba  support traders suna amfani da  high buying volume  (green bar chart ) wajen tabbatar da(  reversal ) juyawar kasuwa zuwa uptrend 
Lokacin da price yataba  resistance traders suna amfani  high selling volume (red bar chart? Wajen tabbatar da (reversal) juyawar kasuwa zuwa downtrend 
BREAKING SUPPORT 'dip 
Lokacin da kasuwa take tafiya a support traders suna amfani da low buying volume (green bar chart ) wajen Gane breaking support Wanda zai qara tura kasuwa zuwa qasa 
BREAKING RESISTANCE
Lokacin da kasuwa take tafiya a resistance traders suna amfani da high buying volume (green bar chart ) wajen gane breaking resistance Wanda zai qara tura kasuwa zuwa sama 
TREND CONFIRMATION 
Lokacin da  market take tafiya uptrend Amma  volume Yana decreasing akwai yiwuwar juyawar kasuwa (bearish reversal) zuwa qasa 
lokacin da market take tafiya downtrend  Amma volume Yana increasing akwai yiwuwar juyawar kasuwa (bullish reversal)  sama 
VOLUME DIVERGENCE 
price yayi forming lower high ' volume yayi forming higher low za'a iya samun reversal zuwa downtrend 
price yayi forming higher low ' volume yayi forming lower high akwai juyawar kasuwa zuwa uptrend '
Another point high volume lokacin uptrend yana qara nuna irin yadda price yake da strength move and low volume lokacin downtrend Yana qara nuna yadda price yake da weak move 
Akwai alamomi dayawa da volume yake dasu wannan da muka kawo zasu iya kasance sune keyaways ' dukkan wani trader akwai tsarin yadda yake gabatar da harkokinsa a kasuwa ' babban nasara shine asamu riba ! 
Allah yabamu sa'a